{"tid":1145054,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"出左黎做野之後，有冇人覺得自己個中文全名越黎越陌生","createTime":"2019-05-08T12:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T12:36:43.000Z","uid":103879,"like":31,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"eb47805ad1cfc46b04f4dcfa0c4f4e066574788f","tid":1145054,"uid":103879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:23:49.000Z","msg":"出左黎做野之後，好似都冇乜機會用到自己既中文全名。<br />\n工作方面通常都會用英文名黎稱呼對方，好似Peter,Paul果d。<br />\n家人方面通常都會叫對方既小名，或者直接叫個身份就算。<br />\n朋友方面通常都會叫對方既花名。<br />\n愛人方面都好少叫對方全名。<br />\n平時收email同信通常都係見到自己英文全名。<br />\n今日我老母無啦啦叫我中文全名，我呆左一秒先識反應。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9d0081e3aca2fa047cd81b2a4285cb90cdae0c","tid":1145054,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f70a39ee8a7f3edbd1acd4dea12a89470f0ccd","tid":1145054,"uid":215864,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:28:00.000Z","msg":"有時做嘢冇啦啦會呆滯幾秒唔知自己喺到做緊咩撚嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80d0d76e92d033b0c040fe76ecd7beabb4ea1b0","tid":1145054,"uid":103879,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:29:00.000Z","msg":"個情況就好似一首自己曾經成日loop既歌，隔左幾年係街邊聽返首歌，會覺得首歌又陌生又熟識<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa500f276f45b5c5f8f3c9681e5f27ac70beeea","tid":1145054,"uid":61543,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:39:54.000Z","msg":"人人都叫我做呀邊個邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d0f03233fa8cd3253bb14d27ef21966ae8540fd","tid":1145054,"uid":103879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1aa500f276f45b5c5f8f3c9681e5f27ac70beeea","tid":1145054,"uid":61543,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T12:39:54.000Z","msg":"人人都叫我做呀邊個邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=